      "cookedHtml": "<p>“Can I reference data from another board in <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000173/smart-spreadsheet-for-monday\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Smart Spreadsheet</a>?”</p>\n<p>One of our customers needed to build formulas across multiple boards: calculate totals, compare values, and work with shared data living in different places. A familiar challenge — your data is spread across boards, but your formulas want everything in one view.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Here’s the workaround with</strong> <strong>Smart Spreadsheet on a Dashboard</strong>.</p>\n<p>How it works:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Add Smart Spreadsheet as a <a href=\"https://docs.stiltsoft.com/ssfm/how-to-insert-smart-spreadsheet-as-a-dashboard-widget-124984515.html\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">dashboard widget</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Connect all the boards you need<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/a/2a11db53cdb6654439f23b9dbc6511a969370033.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/a/2a11db53cdb6654439f23b9dbc6511a969370033_2_690x375.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"375\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1759×956 115 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Click “Import boards” to automatically import all connected boards into the spreadsheet.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/8/784ed0d2ec5478674aa02fe1672ce4601a695e65.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/8/784ed0d2ec5478674aa02fe1672ce4601a695e65_2_690x358.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"358\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1767×919 88.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Build formulas that reference data <strong>across multiple boards</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let’s look at a simple cross-board calculation example using budgets.<br />\nOn <span class=\"bbcode-u\">a separate spreadsheet tab,</span> we calculated the <strong>total planned budget</strong> and <strong>total actual spend</strong> across two different campaign boards using the well-known <code>SUM</code> formula, <span class=\"bbcode-u\">referencing value ranges</span> from the relevant columns on each board.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/9/5938d8ef0242731c027bc408f7d34e13681460c8.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/5/9/5938d8ef0242731c027bc408f7d34e13681460c8_2_690x355.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"355\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1766×911 81.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Then, based on this aggregated data, we built a chart that clearly visualizes the variance between planned and actual costs.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/f/8f2f78559f2ce23fc1d4be09ef6cb871a8c08b57.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/f/8f2f78559f2ce23fc1d4be09ef6cb871a8c08b57_2_690x448.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"448\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1413×919 74.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Thanks to the <strong><a href=\"https://docs.stiltsoft.com/ssfm/smart-spreadseet-two-way-synchronization-with-a-board-182485505.html\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">two-way sync</a></strong>, any change made on a board is automatically recalculated in the spreadsheet — and vice versa.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/6/563d51decb53755bc3477a2df3c41c9576815180.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/5/6/563d51decb53755bc3477a2df3c41c9576815180_2_690x347.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"347\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">911×459 37.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/6/763905e0cad923437e013cf39f1613413a04b471.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/6/763905e0cad923437e013cf39f1613413a04b471_2_690x454.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"454\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1431×942 76.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Your Smart Spreadsheet widget is <strong>live</strong>, so formulas, totals, and charts always reflect the latest data.</p>\n<p>You can <a href=\"https://auth.monday.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=03cc84afdcacd614e3b93f33444c6956&amp;response_type=install\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">install</a> and test <strong>Smart Spreadsheet</strong> for free for 14 days and decide if it works for you.</p>"
